              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Absolute cross section of 14N(d,p) reaction was",
                "determined using previously measured deuteron elastic",
                "scattering cross section on 12C and 14N"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To determine the contribution of carbon to elastic",
                "scattering with melamine target, ratio of the yield",
                "for the 4.4 MeV first excited state in 12C to that for",
                "the 12C ground state for the deuteron scattering by",
                "the carbon target was measured at at all angles. The",
                "elastic nitrogen yield was determined by extracting",
                "the 4.4 MeV yield from the melamine target and",
                "using the yield ratio from the carbon target to",
                "subtract its contribution to the total nitrogen",
                "plus carbon elastic yield."
              ]
            }
          ],
